    <h2><i class="fas fa-download fa-lg color-black"></i> Installation</h2>

    <header>There is many ways to install Pam, choose one of them...</header>

    <section>
        <h3><i class="fab fa-php fa-lg color-blue"></i> Composer Require</h3>

        <p>To get Pam with Composer (recommended), type in the terminal :</p>
        <code>$ composer require philippebeck/pam</code>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3><i class="fab fa-git-alt fa-lg color-tomato"></i> Git Clone</h3>

        <p>To clone the project with Git, run the terminal to type :</p>
        <code>$ git clone https://github.com/philippebeck/pam.git</code>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3><i class="fab fa-github fa-lg color-gh"></i> GitHub Release</h3>

